--[[

# SimpleLite UI Library
Author: YourNameHere (2024)
Version: 1.0

A lightweight modular UI library built from scratch and inspired by earlier UI codebases.
- Executor-agnostic: Works with Synapse, Krnl, Xeno, Fluxus, etc. (auto-detects protection method).
- Modern design, efficient code, and improved maintainability.
- Removable/replaceable features, including re-color.
- Extensible: add your own controls/groupboxes and tabs.
- Built-in "Config" tab kept compatible with original style.
- Various simple components documented below.

--- Usage Example ---

local Library = loadstring(game:HttpGet("your/path/here"))() -- or require if local

-- Create a window
local window = Library:CreateWindow({
    Title = "My Script Hub",
    Size = UDim2.fromOffset(550, 600),
    Center = true,
    AutoShow = true, -- auto opens the UI
})

-- Add a tab
local tab = window:AddTab("Main")

-- Add a left groupbox
local left = tab:AddLeftGroupbox("Main Controls")
left:AddLabel("Hello world!")
left:AddToggle("AutoFarm", {Text="Enable Auto-Farm"}):OnChanged(function(on) print(on) end)
left:AddInput("Nick", {Text="Change Name", Placeholder="Your Name"}):OnChanged(function(txt) print(txt) end)

-- Add a right groupbox
local right = tab:AddRightGroupbox("Settings")
right:AddSlider("WalkSpeed", {Text="WalkSpeed", Min=16, Max=200, Default=16, Rounding=0}):OnChanged(function(v) print(v) end)

-- Add the config tab, which is always available
local configTab = window:AddTab("Config")
-- ... do config stuff as usual (see original documentation for details)

-- See wiki (or this file) for full API

--- Keybinds/Features ---
- Toggle UI: RightCtrl or RightShift (or set Library.ToggleKeybind = ... yourself)
- Dynamic theming & colors
- Watermark, notifications, and keybind frame (see Library:SetWatermark, Library:Notify, etc)

]]

